&lt;New Harding Group Inc>,formerly Harding Carpets Ltd, said it declared its firstdividend since fiscal 1978 of 10 cts per subordinate votingshare and multiple voting share, pay April 15, record April 8.    The company said the dividend establishes a new policy forthe payment of quarterly dividends.    New Harding earlier reported profit of 653,000 dlrs or 19cts a share for first quarter ended January 31. It said priorresults were not comparable due to the company's November, 1986acquisition of a 57 pct stake in Continuous Colour Coat Ltd. Reuter&#3;